Title: Titter: Revolutionizing the Apparel Industry with AI-touched Tweeter

I. Executive Summary

Titter is an innovative AI company that utilizes natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning to create a platform that empowers consumers to easily and securely tweet their desired attire. Our goal is to revolutionize the apparel industry by enabling users to tweet their fantasies and create an AI-powered tweeter that can generate flattering outfits based on real-time user feedback, thus reducing the time and effort required for fashionistas to fashion outfits.
